<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PG/PhD Guide Hub - Welcome</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Georgia:wght@400;700&family=Segoe+UI:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* CSS INTEGRATED DIRECTLY FOR RELIABILITY */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f4f6f8;
            color: #333333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .gateway-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 900px;
            padding: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .uni-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #003366;
            padding-bottom: 1rem;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .uni-header h1 {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            color: #003366;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .uni-header p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #555;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .portal-grid {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            width: 100%;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .portal-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dcdcdc;
            border-top: 4px solid #003366;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            width: 320px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }

        .portal-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .portal-icon {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #003366;
        }

        .portal-card h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #003366;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .portal-card p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .portal-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #003366;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            width: 100%;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }

        /* Admin Specific Styling */
        .portal-card.admin-card {
            border-top: 4px solid #800000;
        }

        .portal-card.admin-card .portal-icon, 
        .portal-card.admin-card h2 {
            color: #800000;
        }

        .portal-card.admin-card .portal-btn {
            background-color: #800000;
        }

        .portal-card.admin-card .portal-btn:hover {
            background-color: #600000;
        }

        .portal-card .portal-btn:hover {
            background-color: #002244;
        }

        .uni-footer {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="gateway-container">
        
        <div class="uni-header">
            <h1>PG/PhD Guide Hub</h1>
            <p>University Research Management System</p>
        </div>

        <div class="portal-grid">
            <a href="https://fst-project-react.vercel.app/" class="portal-card">
                <div class="portal-icon">🎓</div>
                <h2>Student Portal</h2>
                <p>Track milestones and schedule reviews with your assigned research guide.</p>
                <div class="portal-btn">Access Student Hub</div>
            </a>

            <a href="https://fst-project-lac.vercel.app/" class="portal-card admin-card">
                <div class="portal-icon">👨‍🏫</div>
                <h2>Admin / Guide Portal</h2>
                <p>Approve topics and manage all your assigned PhD researchers.</p>
                <div class="portal-btn">Access Guide Dashboard</div>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="uni-footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 University Academic Affairs. Authorized Personnel Only.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>